01:08:38.670 --> 01:08:41.457
Slow wave sleep is critical, however,

01:08:41.457 --> 01:08:43.700
it's critical mostly for motor learning

01:08:43.700 --> 01:08:45.780
and the learning of specific details.

01:08:45.780 --> 01:08:50.320
So REM is kind of emotions and
general themes and meaning,

01:08:50.320 --> 01:08:53.346
and slow wave sleep, motor
learning and details.

